<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Sample response: There are 35 crayons because I skip-counted by 5.</li>
      <li>A 7 by 5 array or a 5 by 7 array.   <m>7\times5</m>= ? or <m>5\times7</m> = ?</li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


